### ====== GET ENDPOINTS ======

### 1. Obtener todos los appointments
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/appointments
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Obtener un appointment por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Listar appointments de un paciente específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/appointments/patient/{{patientId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Listar appointments de un profesional específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/appointments/professional/{{professionalId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



### ====== POST ENDPOINTS ======

### 5. Crear un nuevo appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "{{patientId}}",
  "professionalId": "{{professionalId}}",
  "serviceId": "{{serviceId}}",
  "startTime": "2026-05-15T10:30:00Z",
  "mode": "IN_PERSON"
}

### 6. Confirmar un appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/confirm
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Completar un appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/complete
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Cancelar un appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/cancel
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Marcar un appointment como no-show
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/no-show
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ====== PUT ENDPOINTS ======

### 10. Reagendar un appointment
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/reschedule
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "startTime": "2026-05-20T14:00:00Z"
}

### 11. Registrar link de reunión virtual
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/virtual-link
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "virtualMeetingLink": "https://meet.example.com/room123"
}

### ====== NOTAS ======
# 1. Reemplaza los IDs de ejemplo con IDs válidos de tu base de datos
# 2. Asegúrate de que el servidor esté ejecutándose en http://localhost:8080/api
# 3. Ajusta la URL base (@baseUrl) si el servidor está en un puerto diferente
# 4. Usa Ctrl+Alt+R (Windows) o Cmd+Option+R (Mac) para ejecutar la petición actual
# 5. Los tiempos (startTime) deben estar en formato ISO 8601 (ej: 2026-05-15T10:30:00Z)
# 6. El campo "mode" puede ser: "IN_PERSON" o "VIRTUAL"

